# Novella Dating App - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual API keys

# =============================================================================
# AI CHATBOT API KEYS (Choose one or more - the app will try them in order)
# =============================================================================

# OpenAI API (ChatGPT) - Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# REACT_APP_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here

# Anthropic API (Claude) - Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# REACT_APP_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-anthropic-key-here

# Google Gemini API - Get from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# REACT_APP_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key-here

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
# 1. Choose at least one AI service above
# 2. Get your API key from the respective platform
# 3. Uncomment the line and replace with your actual key
# 4. Restart the development server (npm start)
# 5. The Amora chatbot will automatically use the first available API

# =============================================================================
# API COSTS (as of 2024) - Choose based on your budget
# =============================================================================
# OpenAI GPT-3.5-turbo: ~$0.002 per 1K tokens (cheapest)
# Google Gemini Pro: Free tier available, then ~$0.001 per 1K tokens
# Anthropic Claude: ~$0.003 per 1K tokens (highest quality)

# =============================================================================
# EXAMPLE: If you want to use OpenAI
# =============================================================================
# REACT_APP_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-react-openai-key-here

# =============================================================================
# EXAMPLE: If you want to use Google Gemini (free tier)
# =============================================================================
# REACT_APP_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-react-gemini-key-here
